{"tid":2133547,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"共和黨提法案 准動武阻大陸侵台","createTime":"2020-07-31T07:00:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-31T07:15:11.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"043cb243dde41eef3612f46ef9293215d159cc5f","tid":2133547,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T07:00:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200731/7WFXK3KH5LIBZQLPUWNB3HLI3Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200731%2F7WFXK3KH5LIBZQLPUWNB3HLI3Y%2F&d=LJfbHi1nzQR09hbgKwAG11u%2BYei5PLor89YqF%2FSdhCs%3D&h=cc6ee554\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200731%2F7WFXK3KH5LIBZQLPUWNB3HLI3Y%2F&h=60fd6b1f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200731/7WFXK3KH5LIBZQLPUWNB3HLI3Y/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n共和黨提法案 准動武阻大陸侵台<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/sP-iGczXv30LoDr7e4RtplKO2m4=/720x501/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CIAYALZMHCWEQMWA4U53D34GSY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FsP-iGczXv30LoDr7e4RtplKO2m4%3D%2F720x501%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCIAYALZMHCWEQMWA4U53D34GSY.gif&h=d7771b46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n台海局勢急劇升溫；圖為美軍早前在菲律賓海巡邏。<br />\n<br />\n美國眾議院外委會亞太小組共和黨首席議員約霍（Ted Yoho）當地時間29日提出《防止台灣遭侵略法案》，法案授權美國總統在中國武力犯台時，可動用武力防衞台灣，同時也鼓勵美國總統訪台。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：NBA中國學校被揭教練虐待球員<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鼓勵總統訪台<br />\n<br />\n現時南海及東海風起雲湧，英國廣播公司（BBC）引述專家分析，指中美兩國會爆發戰爭的地點是台灣，而不是南海。文章解釋，原因之一是中國國家主席習近平以民族復興自居，其二是台灣有重大戰略價值，能成為核潛艇基地，解決海南島需要大量海空掩護核潛艇的需求，故中美關係越緊張，中國越急着奪下台灣。中國國防部昨亦透露，海軍航空兵組織轟-6G、轟-6J等新型戰機在南海開展高強度訓練。<br />\n<br />\n約霍提出《防止台灣遭侵略法案》支持台灣，。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，中印緊張局勢仍未化解，。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n中央社"},{"pid":"1ae34811f380de00ccca6be47b4667c194c92cea","tid":2133547,"uid":270220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T07:01:21.000Z","msg":"幾時通過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04f63d402a4a4c047401fd8e9ab819295f847475","tid":2133547,"uid":52609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T07:02:04.000Z","msg":"好似WW2前英國保護波蘭咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05cfd1caf014d4f9536e79b72cbcb5e9ffeac105","tid":2133547,"uid":270220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04f63d402a4a4c047401fd8e9ab819295f847475","tid":2133547,"uid":52609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T07:02:04.000Z","msg":"好似WW2前英國保護波蘭咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T07:03:23.000Z","msg":"想知民主黨會唔會反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db8feb78bfdfad40de63f1bcd175ac2ea5656172","tid":2133547,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T07:03:41.000Z","msg":"共和黨真心反共"},{"pid":"0f5c6d9ddacd478f7b986a142dc73d9baf8932b5","tid":2133547,"uid":270220,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"db8feb78bfdfad40de63f1bcd175ac2ea5656172","tid":2133547,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T07:03:41.000Z","msg":"共和黨真心反共"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T07:04:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gwPs44m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgwPs44m.jpg&h=79b983e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係滅共呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d86d2b93b1846c8665ded49fd4f5741eabe36b0","tid":2133547,"uid":25858,"lik